'''米高·莊臣'''，常譯為'''米高·莊遜'''（{{lang-en|'''Michael Johnson'''}}，{{bd|1988年|2月24日|catidx=Johnson, Michael}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，擔任[[中場|中場]]，現時自由身。

==俱乐部生涯==
雖然米高·莊臣自幼支持[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]，但卻是[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]的學徒球員。2004年[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]把米高·莊臣簽下<ref name="programme">{{cite news | title=In Reserve: Michael Johnson | work=Manchester City v Newcastle United Match programme | date=2006-02-01 }}</ref>，成為曼城青年隊的主力，助球隊進入[[英格蘭足總青年盃|英格蘭足總青年盃]]決賽。米高·莊臣的出色表現助他於2006年獲得一隊上陣機會，獲發33號球衣。2006年10月21日，他首次參加[[英超|英超]]，曼城最終以4-0擊敗[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]。自2007/08年球季開始，米高·莊臣改穿6號球衣，但於2007年未因[[腹|腹]]傷而缺陣至翌年2月，期間更進行雙層網膜疝氣修補[[手術|手術]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.mcfc.co.uk/News/Team-news/2008/April/Johnson-hopes-for-strong-finish |title=Johnson hopes for strong finish |publisher=[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|''mcfc.co.uk'']] |date=2008-04-10 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308032701/http://www.mcfc.co.uk/news/team-news/2008/april/johnson-hopes-for-strong-finish |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但於翌季季初腹傷舊患復發，餘下球季就此報銷，他於2008年9月16日與曼城續約五年至2013年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7620053.stm |title=Johnson agrees new Man City deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-09-16 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202095040/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7620053.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009/10年球季米高·莊臣短暫復出，但不久便因於操練時觸傷[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.mcfc.co.uk/News/Team-news/2009/December/Michael-Johnson-injury-blow |title=Michael Johnson injury blow |publisher=[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|''mcfc.co.uk'']] |date=2009-12-10 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2009-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091213121557/http://www.mcfc.co.uk/News/Team-news/2009/December/Michael-Johnson-injury-blow |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再次回到傷兵陣營<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/8407154.stm |title=Man City's Michael Johnson to miss rest of season |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-12-11 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2018-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181101022603/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/8407154.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年3月米高·莊臣涉嫌於去年12月在[[曼徹斯特|曼徹斯特]]一所[[夜總會|夜總會]]，以頭撞一名[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]球迷而遭受警方調查<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/8546955.stm |title=Manchester City star quizzed on United fan 'head butt' |publisher=[[BBC|''BBC News'']] |date=2010-03-03 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307140621/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/8546955.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年4月7日米高·莊臣表示有信心其十字韌帶傷勢可趕及於季前操練復原<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/8607757.stm |title=Michael Johnson targets pre-season return for Man City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-04-07 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307020323/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/8607757.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他未能再在現時曼城億萬大軍名單中佔一席位，於2011年1月表示希望可以獲得機會外借以爭取回復狀態<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/9359345.stm |title=Manchester City's Michael Johnson considers loan move |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-12 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307050336/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/9359345.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年7月28日米高·莊臣獲借用到由舊上司[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|艾歷臣]]領軍的[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]，為期一整個球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14329051.stm |title=Leicester City sign midfielder Michael Johnson |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-28 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |archive-date=2011-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111024220903/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14329051.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

